OL,3,CPolice stood down after bus station
OL,4,Ccordoned off due to suspicious bags
OL,6,FPart of Jersey's Liberation Bus
OL,7,FStation was cordoned off on Wednesday
OL,8,Flunchtime after two suitcases were
OL,9,Fleft unattended.
OL,11,FOfficers from the States of Jersey
OL,12,FPolice responded following a report of
OL,13,Fsome unsupervised luggage outside the
OL,14,Fterminal in St Helier.
OL,16,FLibertyBus cordoned off the pavement
OL,17,Fwaiting area while specially trained
OL,18,Fofficers carefully checked through the
OL,19,Fbags.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/2
