OL,3,CPolice stood down after bus station
OL,4,Ccordoned off due to suspicious bags
OL,6,FNo threat was found and the area has
OL,7,Fsince reopened, with the luggage
OL,8,Fhanded into lost and found.
OL,10,FThe police response has been stood
OL,11,Fdown and buses are running as usual.
